OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly cloudy and mainly dry
OL,6,Fthis morning, although some patchy
OL,7,Flight drizzle is possible at first. A
OL,8,Fbrighter but noticeably breezy
OL,9,Fafternoon for many. Some warm sunshine
OL,10,Fdeveloping, the best of this likely in
OL,11,Fthe north of the region.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry, though still rather
OL,14,Fbreezy this evening. Plenty of late
OL,15,Fsunshine around, though coastal parts
OL,16,Fof Sussex could stay largely cloudy
OL,17,Funtil after dusk. Fine, dry overnight
OL,18,Fwith winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
