OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA dry, sunny day on
OL,6,FSaturday. Feeling slightly warmer and
OL,7,Fnot as windy compared to recent days.
OL,8,
OL,9,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FPatchy
OL,10,Fovernight mist and fog clears to
OL,11,Fanother dry, bright and rather warm
OL,12,Fday on Sunday. Similar Monday and
OL,13,FTuesday, likely dry and slightly
OL,14,Fwarmer. Mainly light winds.
